title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 141-3.7 - "All other" employees
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 141-3.7 - "All other" employees

State Regulations
"All other" employees
means all building
service employees other than janitors in residential
buildings. Notes
